## MutableKeys type

Get mutable property keys of T.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export type MutableKeys<T> = Exclude<Keys<T>, ReadonlyKeys<T>>
```
**References:** [Keys](./types-kit.keys.md)<!-- -->, [ReadonlyKeys](./types-kit.readonlykeys.md)

## Example


```ts
interface Props {
     readonly a?: number
     b: number
     readonly c: number
   }
   // Expect: 'b'
   type Keys = ReadonlyKeys<Props>
```
